return ['messages'=>['
<p>It came as no surprise that cigarette butts are the world’s most littered trash. Cigarette butts are a form of non-biodegradable litter, which cause significant harm to the natural environment. They are toxic. They are pollution. They are everywhere – and the problem is that they are very difficult to be cleaned.</p>



<p>Cleaning up cigarette butt litter is a powerful way to fight pollution – community engagement is the key. The Butt Litter Clean-Up Event is organised by The Lok Sin Tong Benevolent Society, Kowloon, aiming at promoting a smoke-free healthy lifestyle through walking and cleaning up butt litter along the beautiful promenades. Thanks to our people, who volunteered in this clean-up event on 11 March.</p>
'=>'<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>烟头是世界上被丢弃最多的垃圾，这一点并不奇怪。烟头是一种不可生物降解的垃圾，对自然环境造成严重危害。它们有毒。它们是污染。它们无处不在--问题是它们很难被清理。    </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>清理烟蒂垃圾是消除污染的有效方法--社区参与是关键。清理烟蒂垃圾活动由九龙乐善堂慈善会主办，旨在通过沿美丽的海滨步行清理烟蒂垃圾，推广无烟健康生活方式。感谢大家在 3 月 11 日参与这项清洁活动。  </p>
<!-- /wp:group -->','<p>28 volunteers in total, including their family members, participated in this two-hour event at the Tsim Sha Tsui – Hunghom Promenade, a 3.5-kilometre-long viewing trail along the coast with the magnificent view of Victoria Harbour and the dramatic view of Hong Kong Island skyline. Starting from the Tsim Sha Tsui Star Ferry Pier, our volunteers picked up every butt litter that they spotted all along the promenade. They carefully removed the butts as many as they could, and they even cleaned the dock stairs at the pier to prevent the toxic butt litter from being washed into our harbour. We believe cleaning up butt litter also helps create a welcoming and beautiful city.</p>
<p>We truly appreciate the aims of the Butt Clean-Up Event - beautifying the city while also promoting health and wellness for the community. It was a great event to participate in and it was very rewarding. We would like to thank our people who helped make this a valuable experience. Great teamwork at its best – collecting hundreds of cigarette butts. Every one of us can make a change for this beautiful city – as long as we are willing to serve our community and connect with one another.</p>'=>'<p>尖沙咀-红磡海滨长廊是一条长达 3.5 公里的沿岸观景步道，沿途可饱览维多利亚港的壮丽景色和香港岛的壮观天际线。我们的志愿者从尖沙咀天星码头出发，捡拾海滨长廊上的每一个烟头垃圾。他们小心翼翼地将烟蒂尽可能多地清理掉，甚至还清理了码头的阶梯，以防止有毒的烟蒂垃圾被冲入我们的海港。我们相信，清理烟头垃圾也有助于创建一个温馨美丽的城市。   </p>
<p>我们非常欣赏 "屁股大扫除 "活动的宗旨--在美化城市的同时促进社区的健康和保健。这是一次非常有意义的活动。我们要感谢我们的员工，是他们让这次活动成为一次宝贵的经历。伟大的团队合作发挥到了极致--收集了数百个烟头。我们每个人都可以为这座美丽的城市带来改变--只要我们愿意为社区服务并相互联系。    </p>','Our Sustainability Journey'=>'我们的可持续发展之旅','dailymotion_url-video-0011d75'=>'https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb','editor-text-editor-e5a92ba'=>'<!-- wp:paragraph -->
